<p>We also have a legitimate interest in using Google Font to optimise our online service. The corresponding legal basis for this is <strong>Art. 6 para. 1 lit. f GDPR (legitimate interests)</strong>. Nevertheless, we only use Google Font if you have given your consent to it.</p>
